{"tid":729240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青年亮槍：疑犯Fb晒槍 「我要做阿SIR」","createTime":"2018-07-04T11:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T13:03:37.000Z","uid":147522,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d78a2d56efe5cb95b774b2837a36667462fb6636","tid":729240,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:25:50.000Z","msg":"涉嫌「持有仿製槍械」被捕的青年姓林，22歲，據悉，他與家人同住上水區，2年前中六畢業後讀進修課程，之後到地盤工作。消息指，林在數月前被辭退，疑因此受到打擊，精神開始出現異常，親友亦有察覺，但未知他有否求醫。據了解，他早前到外地旅行時，購入今次涉案的氣槍。<br />\n<br />\n在林的社交網站Facebook專頁，他自稱曾就讀嶺南大學，狀態為「戀愛中」，於上月19日曾發帖指「幾時有機會再玩&hellip;我要做阿SIR」，表示感到有挑戰性，同時上載一張氣槍照片，該支槍與今日警方檢獲的氣槍外形相似。另他又上載多張身穿地盤工作服的照片，以及多張自拍照，表現充滿自信。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/192548_4671905f8bb392d5f251bd6b3ebe07c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F192548_4671905f8bb392d5f251bd6b3ebe07c8.png&h=a0c094ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d41f916ed68b9ec77ae78992e411d465f440b651","tid":729240,"uid":188,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:27:41.000Z","msg":"乜佢都幾忠心 著住件地盤臭衫 返工收工都唔換"},{"pid":"cf36c4f6270fcb7134da36f94116d2ceef7673bc","tid":729240,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"我迫不及待好想玩玩了"},{"pid":"7205fd3edee3028d0c4abdfc229caf79804735c2","tid":729240,"uid":6352,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"毅進仔果然心智唔成熟"},{"pid":"b113ba04dd17c179a99744c680dee16530f35ecd","tid":729240,"uid":41974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:32:30.000Z","msg":"地盤佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b45b675721329a0d6cfdcddda0d93c496183137","tid":729240,"uid":7837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:32:45.000Z","msg":"有加入警隊嘅潛力<img src=\"/assets/faces